==Serbian==
===Greeting===
'''Христос васкрсе'''
#[[Happy Easter]]
#(''literally''): [[Christ]] [[is|was]] [[resurrect|resurrected]] or [[Christ]] [[rise|rose]].
*:''Note:  This is only the first part of the greeting.  The reply from the other person or persons, completes the greeting.  For the reply, see [[Ваистину васкрсе]].''
